snippet.title: Mega Drive Longplay [475] Winter Challenge
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: JagOfTroy

Probably one of the worst Olympic games I've ever played.
Incredibly slow and delayed controls, no instructions whatsoever or indication for what you should do. -
